  "prompt": "What can you wear a Santa hat with?",
  "response": "A Santa hat is a versatile and festive accessory that can be paired with a wide range of outfits to add a cheerful holiday vibe. Here are some ideas for what to wear with a Santa hat:\n\n### Casual Outfits  \n- **Cozy Sweaters**: Pair the hat with a chunky knit sweater, jeans, and boots for a comfortable, winter-ready look.  \n- **Hoodies and Sweatshirts**: Add a Santa hat to a casual hoodie or graphic sweatshirt for a laid-back holiday style.  \n- **Leggings and Oversized Tees**: Combine with leggings, an oversized T-shirt, and sneakers for an easy, festive outfit.  \n- **Pajamas**: Wear it with your favorite holiday-themed pajamas for a cozy Christmas morning look.\n\n### Dressy Outfits  \n- **Holiday Party Attire**: Pair the Santa hat with a sequin dress, velvet jumpsuit, or glittery skirt for a festive party look.  \n- **Blazers and Dresses**: Add a touch of whimsy to a sleek blazer, dress, or skirt suit.  \n- **Festive Accessories**: Complement the hat with sparkly jewelry, a clutch, or holiday-themed shoes.  \n\n### Themed Outfits  \n- **Ugly Christmas Sweaters**: A Santa hat is the perfect finishing touch to a quirky Christmas sweater.  \n- **Matching Red and White**: Coordinate the hat with a red or white outfit for a cohesive holiday look.  \n- **Costumes**: Wear it as part of a full Santa Claus costume or with elf-inspired attire.  \n\n### Outerwear  \n- **Winter Coats**: Pair the hat with a cozy peacoat, puffer jacket, or wool coat for a festive winter ensemble.  \n- **Scarves and Gloves**: Match the hat with red, white, or green scarves and gloves for a coordinated look.  \n\n### Accessories  \n- **Santa Hat and Sunglasses**: Add a playful twist by pairing the hat with sunglasses for a cool, holiday vibe.  \n- **Santa Hat and Beanie**: Double up on warmth by wearing the Santa hat over a beanie for an extra cozy look.  \n\nThe Santa hat is all about fun and festivity, so don\u2019t be afraid to get creative and wear it in a way that makes you feel merry and bright! \ud83c\udf85\ud83c\udf84",
  "temperature": 1.0,
